{"tid":1301593,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢果陣都要做好保護 黎入黎睇下啦","createTime":"2019-07-09T16:34:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T14:16:54.000Z","uid":43100,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"43796df16dde4fe1314d4a973bece704623e59bf","tid":1301593,"uid":43100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:34:06.000Z","msg":"#014 個人防護裝備 Personal Protective Equipment (PPE)<br />\n<br />\n今集想同各位講講地盤常用既個人防護裝備 首先咩係PPE呢 PPE係指 &ldquo;所有供個人在工作時穿著或使用的裝備（包括在惡劣天氣下穿著的方服），而這些裝備是保護個人免受一種或多種的安全或健康危害&rdquo; (From 職業安全健康局網址) 今集會簡介下各類PPE<br />\n<br />\n1.安全帽<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EYbjmYx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEYbjmYx.jpg&h=edf4de3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n首先就講下地盤佬既象徵&mdash;&mdash;安全帽先 圖入面有安全帽既主要部分 咁每個部分既用途就唔詳細講啦 直接睇圖啦 每個配件既用途都唔同 就唔一一講解啦 有興趣可以睇下之後果張圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gUiUVix.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgUiUVix.jpg&h=2f667979&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另外都同大家介紹下 其實安全帽都有好多種 就好似呢張圖咁 係唔同既地方可以有更加多既選擇啊<br />\n講多句 其實安全帽都有好多種頻色 地盤常用既係白及黃色 其實都無咩特別分別 係除左藍色多數係訊號員用之外 其他各種顏色都無咩特別<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g7O51Yy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg7O51Yy.jpg&h=37b12109&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n詳細版 有時間又有興趣可以自己望下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.護目鏡<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VfuUaRP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVfuUaRP.jpg&h=a6c6438a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n護目鏡當然係用黎保護對眼啦 眼呢好脆弱既 係地盤做野好多時都有D碎石飛黎飛去 咁護目鏡就好有需要啦 廢時D碎石打中眼啊 <br />\n不過其實護目鏡就無咩特別需知既 唯一要提既就係買鏡果陣要根據你既用途去揀合適既護目鏡 詳情請參考下圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j9U1Aiu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj9U1Aiu.jpg&h=a38c7bf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n自己睇 自己諗下你既用途再揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.手套<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jJWn4bQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjJWn4bQ.jpg&h=4cc66062&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n講起手套 相信好多人都會諗去最常用既勞工手套 但係你地又有無諗過 其實手套係有分好多種? 而手套既材料係可以用到棉 樹膠 尼龍 皮革等 係唔同既時候記得揀下唔同既手套啊!<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1pHFQRQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1pHFQRQ.jpg&h=42ff08e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n防震手套好似幾好用咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4.口罩及其他呼吸防護裝備<br />\n我懶啦唔打字 直接去圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OPiBpbR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOPiBpbR.jpg&h=e319ee18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唯一要提醒既係 如果用N95口罩果D 記得要戴到緊貼住塊面 我發夢果陣係見到好多人都無做到呢點 咁個口罩其實同戴普通防飛沬口罩無分別 所以如果一見到唔對路 記得即刻戴好個口罩<br />\n<br />\n5.安全鞋<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3K0Trqb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3K0Trqb.jpg&h=83a946e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n姐係鞋尖同鞋底都有鋼片既鞋 可以保護腳板 好有用 非常建議發夢落地盤著住佢~~~ 照舊 我懶啦 自己睇圖啦<br />\n揀安全鞋記得諗下自己既用途 安全鞋有分防滑鞋底 絕緣鞋底 防高溫低溫既鞋底等 記得諗清楚你既用途再去作出選擇啊 <br />\n發夢果陣其實一對安全鞋係可以有好多用途 一黎可以避免俾人認鞋 二黎有咩野都可以用對鞋黎踢開佢<br />\n另外 如果無著慣安全鞋既人有機會唔習慣 有巴打建議可以試下買大一個碼 當然 最好係買鞋果陣先試著下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎俾下意見"},{"pid":"19128aea07b8d3eb0c5f96ce225688b35b2658f3","tid":1301593,"uid":43100,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:34:26.000Z","msg":"小弟開左個channel 同埋group 希望可以分享下各類工程知識俾其他同路人 希望可以令佢地發個好夢 訓得安心d<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://t.me/engineernoextradition \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fengineernoextradition%20&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBCVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=25b91d8f\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/engineernoextradition </a><br />\n會定期分享工程類知識<br />\n仲有個group<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://t.me/engineernoextraditionchat \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fengineernoextraditionchat%20&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBCVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=9e558740\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/engineernoextraditionchat </a>"},{"pid":"9aa202ced0673fb05fe91ecc61daa051247a8883","tid":1301593,"uid":43100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:35:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"66f64b1958f94acd2661ce48c01608afc0eea66c","tid":1301593,"uid":43100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:35:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f08a7617199f7cfe4675af0318ef9cdd52b4d3b7","tid":1301593,"uid":43100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:35:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a719e6ccafc588d85ef47c93ceddf67d98cbcebe","tid":1301593,"uid":43100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:36:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d2fcf20beb6febefe6857caa92fb50f08a07fa0b","tid":1301593,"uid":43100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:36:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dbf895785e48acf2bb6039d249b8ca39022483ce","tid":1301593,"uid":43100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:36:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"040fed443ae9209f91aa024805d7e9ea5d8e050d","tid":1301593,"uid":43100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:36:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a647dffcc784b517123f239d7ca3641cf64b401d","tid":1301593,"uid":43100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:36:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"380144730fa2ef6ce13dc45bafed2856942012b6","tid":1301593,"uid":43100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:37:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6e2bfe32ca26f0d8ee4956ae118ae48a0c78f133","tid":1301593,"uid":43100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:37:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6da3213d3c8f49c5f572d15185728f13fd9b2caa","tid":1301593,"uid":43100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:38:01.000Z","ms